            div(class="faq__inner")
                h2(class="feature__title feature__title--1") FAQ
                div(class="item")
                    h3 How does SiYuan store data?
                    p The data is saved in the workspace folder, in the workspace data folder:
                    ul
                        li
                            code assets
                            |  is used to save all inserted assets
                        li
                            code emojis
                            |  is used to save emoji images
                        li
                            code snippets
                            |  is used to save code snippets
                        li
                            code storage
                            |  is used to save named criteria and flashcards, etc.
                        li
                            code templates
                            |  is used to save template snippets
                        li
                            code widgets
                            |  is used to save widgets
                        li
                            code plugins
                            |  is used to save plugins
                        li
                            code public
                            |  is used to save public data
                        li The rest of the folders are the notebook folders created by the user, files with the suffix of <code>.sy</code> in the notebook folder are used to save the document data, and the data format is JSON
                div(class="item")
                    h3 Is SiYuan open source?
                    p SiYuan is completely open source, and contributions are welcome:
                    ul
                        li
                            a(href="https://github.com/siyuan-note/siyuan" target="_blank" class="download__link") User Interface and Kernel
